                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p><addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee>,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">I send you a<lb/> Circular of a school in
                                        which<lb/> I am hereafter to be engaged, and<lb/> take the
                                        liberty of asking your<lb/> influence in my behalf. In
                                        doing<lb/> so, I feel perfectly assured we<lb/> shall merit
                                        your confidence.<lb/> On entering this school, I am<lb/>
                                        altogether satisfied with the<lb/> operations of this
                                        Institution,<lb/> the system being the same<lb/> as that of
                                        the Troy Seminary,<lb/> and <persName>Mrs.
                                        Phelps</persName>' of <placeName>Maryland</placeName>.<lb/>
                                        The teachers in every depart-</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>-ment, are there of <add>?</add>,<lb/> experience and
                                        faithfulness;â€”<lb/> the advantages enjoyed in<lb/>
                                        <add>?</add>, are hardly second to<lb/> a <add>?</add>
                                        school. Excuse the<lb/> liberty I have taken, and<lb/>
                                        believe me, I should not<lb/> have <add>?</add>entured, had
                                        I not<lb/> been fully aware of your<lb/> kind and
                                        benevolent<lb/> character.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">Truly yours</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">E. C.
                                        Barton</persName>.</p>
                              <p>
                                        <date>June 19<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1852</date>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
